<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Assam–Nagaland Border Monitoring System</title>

  <!-- Fonts & Icons -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header id="main-header" class="header">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
          <div class="assam-gov-brand">
            <!-- ASSAC Logo (Primary) -->
            <img src="/image/assac-logo.png" alt="ASSAC Logo" class="assac-logo">

            <div class="brand-text">
              <span class="assac-title">Assam State Space Application Centre</span>
              <span class="portal-title">Assam–Nagaland Border Monitoring Portal</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>



        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
          <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
        </button>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto align-items-center">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#">Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#datasets">Datasets</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#features">Monitoring Tools</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item ms-3">
              <a href="/admin/home" class="btn-login">
                <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Admin
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-8">
          <div class="hero-content text-center">
            <h1>Assam–Nagaland Border Monitoring Portal</h1>
            <p class="lead">
              A geospatial monitoring system for continuous observation of the
              Assam–Nagaland interstate border using multi-year LULC data, satellite imagery,
              change detection, and analytical reporting tools.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
              <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i class="fas fa-map"></i> Open Dashboard
              </a>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#aboutProjectModal">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About Project
              </a>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Project Modal -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="aboutProjectModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered modal-dialog-scrollable">
      <div class="modal-content about-modal">

        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title">
            Development of Comprehensive Change & Encroachment Detection System
            for Assam–Nagaland Interstate Border
          </h5>
          <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
        </div>

        <div class="modal-body">
          <p class="modal-intro">
            The project titled <strong>“Development of Comprehensive Change &
              Encroachment Detection System for Assam–Nagaland Interstate Border”</strong>
            is an initiative of the Border Protection & Development Department,
            Government of Assam.
          </p>

          <h6>Project Objective</h6>
          <p>
            The objective of the project is to develop a comprehensive geospatial
            system for identification, monitoring, and assessment of changes and
            potential encroachments along the Assam–Nagaland interstate boundary
            using satellite imagery and spatial analysis techniques.
          </p>

          <h6>Project Scope</h6>
          <ul class="modal-list">
            <li>Development of a geospatial change and encroachment detection system</li>
            <li>Multi-year satellite imagery analysis for border monitoring</li>
            <li>Land Use and Land Cover (LULC) mapping and change assessment</li>
            <li>Raster comparison and swipe-based visual analysis</li>
            <li>Generation of analytical outputs, statistics, and monitoring reports</li>
          </ul>

          <h6>Implementation Agency</h6>
          <p>
            The project is being implemented by the Assam State Space Application
            Centre (ASSAC) as the technical executing agency, in support of
            government monitoring and decision-making.
          </p>
        </div>




        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- Data Counts Section -->
  <section class="data-counts" id="datasets">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Monitoring Coverage</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Temporal datasets and analytical outputs for border surveillance</p>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="count-card">
            <div class="count-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
            </div>
            <h3><%= userItems.rastercount %></h3>
            <p>Raster Datasets</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="count-card">
            <div class="count-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <h3><%= userItems.lulccount %></h3>
            <p>LULC Layers</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="count-card">
            <div class="count-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            </div>
            <h3><%= userItems.lulcchange %></h3>
            <p>LULC Change Layers</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="count-card">
            <div class="count-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
            </div>
            <h3><%= userItems.hotspotcount %></h3>
            <p>Hotspot Layers</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section id="features" class="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Monitoring Capabilities</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Tools for continuous border observation and analysis</p>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Border Surveillance</h4>
            <p>Continuous geospatial monitoring of the Assam–Nagaland border using time-series satellite
              data.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Year-wise LULC Monitoring</h4>
            <p>Assessment of land use and land cover dynamics and land cover change patterns.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Raster Comparison & Swipe</h4>
            <p>Swipe and comparison tools for visual inspection of multi-temporal satellite imagery.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Analytics & Reports</h4>
            <p>Report charts, area statistics, distance measurements, and downloadable monitoring
              reports.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer id="about" class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row footer-main">
        <!-- Quick Links -->
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 footer-boxes">
          <h5 class="footer-title">Quick Links</h5>
